        public static boolean save(java.lang.Object o,
                           java.lang.String path,
                           java.lang.String fileName,
                           java.lang.String extension)
                    throws java.io.IOException
        Save an object to file.
        Parameters:
        o - Object to save
        path - Directory to save to (will be created if nonexistent)
        fileName - Name of file to save to (will be created until the path)
        extension - Extension of the file to save to
        Returns:
